  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You concentrate aether into yourself, overloading your internal systems and exploding in a blaze of glory. You are immediately slain, and all creatures in a 20-foot-radius around you take 12d6 fire damage.</p><p>If you are a blue mage, instead of being immediately slain, you are knocked unconscious at Dying 2. Abilities that would trigger upon you hitting 0 HP or gaining the Dying condition do not trigger from Self-Destruct.</p><p>If you have the ice or lightning trait, the spell loses the fire trait and instead deals ice or lightning damage and gains the ice or lightning trait, respectively.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 4d6.</p>"
    },
